    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Of a device, instrument, information storage, or other applications, operating according to the principles or methods of electronics, such as having a transistor, microchip, or electron tube. For appliances or instruments that are powered by electricity, use "electric."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
